{"tid":1944613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失3成視角手足疑為神經創傷","createTime":"2020-03-26T13:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T15:14:06.000Z","uid":134087,"like":35,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"ab82584e9c1e7da10963144a55917ad19900eedd","tid":1944613,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"【左眼失3成視角還押人士最新情況】<br />\n上周，本人探監期間接觸到一名男子被警方拘捕後，遭受警方極粗暴毆打，以黑布蒙頭毆打超過5分鐘，導致左眼3成視角受損，更需留院接近一星期。<br />\n<br />\n今日，本人再度探望還押手足，他目前左眼情況未有好轉，預計四月中到醫院覆診。醫生初步診斷為神經創傷，未知會否造成永久創傷。目前男子仍還押當中，未能保釋。<br />\n<br />\n國泰民安 人道支援 會繼續跟進，並支援其他還押義士及家屬。<br />\n<br />\n祈求平安順利，感謝大家。<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民<br />\n大埔區議員<br />\n黃兆健<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/91064160_1091450307879043_6847350395895808000_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=DoocA6nTd68AX9BatVZ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=79ec900c7e159360257350867f2306b3&amp;oe=5EA30E0E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F91064160_1091450307879043_6847350395895808000_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DDoocA6nTd68AX9BatVZ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D79ec900c7e159360257350867f2306b3%26oe%3D5EA30E0E&h=dc93402b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wongsiukinwtt/posts/1091456747878399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwongsiukinwtt%2Fposts%2F1091456747878399&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=fa790d08\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wongsiukinwtt/posts/1091456747878399</a>"},{"pid":"ce7aa7d0455520bdbebf5811d52eaa04a336101c","tid":1944613,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:50:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ebb489427cc8e7933e711bf28f49ff27bfcbcf20","tid":1944613,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:50:35.000Z","msg":"黑警點對人, 一定會有報應<img s